 care. You can ring-fence yourself from the US and solve your securities-la=
w problems, but that doesn=E2=80=99t work for your money-laundering or sanc=
tions problems.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The SEC can=E2=80=
=99t put you in jail, but the Justice Department can.</li>
</ol>
